<br>
Thanks for your support Sensei.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uclindfor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>clindfor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 171<br> <font color=#660000>(12/11/01 5:12:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1472.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> yes</span><hr size=1> I never thougth about it this way! Our fists should really have INSANE criticals to make up for the bad dmg.<br>
